00:14:37,467 --> 00:14:38,400
<i> Jade...</i>

231
00:14:39,767 --> 00:14:41,267
<i> Magiging akin ka ba...</i>

232
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,733
<i> matalik na kaibigan muli?</i>

233
00:14:45,967 --> 00:14:47,167
<i> Talaga?</i>

234
00:14:47,333 --> 00:14:49,000
<i>- Oo.
- Hahawakan kita niyan.</i>

235
00:14:49,133 --> 00:14:51,300
<i>Kahit anong mangyari,
mananatili tayong magkaibigan.</i>

236
00:14:51,433 --> 00:14:53,067
<i> Oo, mananatili kaming magkaibigan.</i>

237
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,567
<i>- Pangako.
- Magkaibigan magpakailanman.</i>

238
00:14:58,033 --> 00:15:04,833
["PAANO KUNG TAYO NA LANG"
MAGPATULOY]

239
00:15:13,133 --> 00:15:15,633
Sigurado ka bang hindi
gusto mo ng umuwi?

240
00:15:16,900 --> 00:15:18,333
Oo, Tatay.

241
00:15:18,633 --> 00:15:19,967
Umuwi ka nang wala ako.

242
00:15:20,067 --> 00:15:22,000
May meeting ka bukas.

243
00:15:22,133 --> 00:15:25,000
At least, gagamit ka
ng iyong go-bag

244
00:15:25,133 --> 00:15:27,133
para sa hindi mo planado
paglalakbay sa kamping.

245
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:30,433
Tatay, pinagtatawanan mo ba ako?

246
00:15:30,533 --> 00:15:33,167
Syempre hindi.
Hindi ko gagawin iyon.

247
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,833
Text mo na lang ako kapag nakuha mo na
busted, okay?

248
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,133
- Tatay.
- Nagbibiro lang ako.

249
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,800
Hindi ko lang mapagkakatiwalaan ang lalaking iyon
kasama si Jade.

250
00:15:46,933 --> 00:15:49,467
Lagi silang nagkakaproblema
kapag magkasama sila.

251
00:15:53,767 --> 00:15:56,400
Sige. Mag-ingat ka.

252
00:15:56,567 --> 00:15:57,700
mauuna na ako.

253
00:15:57,833 --> 00:15:59,200
I-post mo ako, okay?

254
00:15:59,333 --> 00:16:06,367
[PAGPAPALAGOT SA MUSIC PLAY]

255
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:12,900
Lola?

256
00:16:14,767 --> 00:16:16,367
Naririnig mo ba ako?

257
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,700
Lolo Nando?

258
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:25,067
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

259
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:26,367
Lola Sita?

260
00:16:26,467 --> 00:16:28,433
[MABAY-BAY NA KINAKASAN]

261
00:16:30,033 --> 00:16:32,367
Oh! Sabi nila oo!

262
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:36,067
Lola?

263
00:16:37,233 --> 00:16:38,567
[CHESKA]
Sabi nila oo ulit.

264
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:45,167
[Nagpe-play ng Penssive MUSIC]

265
00:16:46,067 --> 00:16:48,633
- P...
- P...

266
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:51,133
- [CHESKA] P...
- Ako...

267
00:16:52,267 --> 00:16:53,300
K?

268
00:16:53,467 --> 00:16:54,633
[CHESKA] Ako...

269
00:16:57,467 --> 00:17:00,133
<i> - Pikit</i> (Close)? Isara?
- Isara?

270
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:02,600
- Isara.
- [CHESKA] Isara.

271
00:17:02,767 --> 00:17:04,100
Isara.

272
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,600
Hmm!

273
00:17:11,433 --> 00:17:12,733
M...

274
00:17:14,133 --> 00:17:15,433
<i>- Ma...
- Ma...</i>

275
00:17:16,767 --> 00:17:18,933
<i>...ta. Pikit-mata
(Nakapikit ang mga mata)!</i>

276
00:17:19,033 --> 00:17:21,133
- Mata.
- Ipikit mo ang iyong mga mata?

277
00:17:22,333 --> 00:17:24,800
Dapat ko bang ipikit ang aking mga mata?

278
00:17:28,033 --> 00:17:29,467
[CHESKA]
Oo! Oo, sabi nila oo.

279
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:31,067
Okay, okay.
Ipikit mo lang ang iyong mga mata,

280
00:17:31,167 --> 00:17:33,633
tapos hawakan ang mga kamay namin.

281
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:35,833
Babasahin namin ito para sa iyo, okay?

282
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,567
Ipikit mo ang iyong mga mata ngayon.
Ayan, tahan na.

283
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,633
Sige magtanong ka.

284
00:17:49,733 --> 00:17:51,800
[RAPHIE]
Ay, oo, sir?

285
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:53,833
Maaari ba akong mag-order?

286
00:17:53,967 --> 00:17:56,133
Oo, sir.
Naghahain pa kami ng drinks.

287
00:17:56,233 --> 00:17:57,867
Hmm, sige.
Isang beer, pakiusap.

288
00:17:58,033 --> 00:18:00,300
Okay, isang beer.

289
00:18:07,233 --> 00:18:09,167
Eto na.

290
00:18:10,367 --> 00:18:13,267
Salamat. Para lang matulungan akong matulog.

291
00:18:13,367 --> 00:18:16,033
Pero di ba medyo maaga
para sa huling tawag?

292
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,367
Oh! Oo, sir.

293
00:18:18,533 --> 00:18:21,167
Maaga kaming nagsara dahil
ng bisita kanina.

294
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:23,167
May iba ka bang gusto?

295
00:18:23,367 --> 00:18:25,900
Hindi, magaling ako.
Ayokong mahirapan ka.

296
00:18:26,067 --> 00:18:28,833
- Ano ang nangyari sa bisita?
- Ay...

297
00:18:28,933 --> 00:18:30,700
Medyo magulo, sir.

298
00:18:30,833 --> 00:18:32,667
Masyado silang nainom.

299
00:18:32,767 --> 00:18:33,667
Ngunit lahat ng ito ay pinangangasiwaan.

300
00:18:33,833 --> 00:18:36,700
Sir Gio at Sir Martin
inalagaan ito kanina.

301
00:18:36,833 --> 00:18:39,567
Ang gaganda ng mga boss ko
hands-on sa mga ganyang bagay.

302
00:18:39,733 --> 00:18:40,967
Gio?

303
00:18:41,067 --> 00:18:42,333
Martin?

304
00:18:42,433 --> 00:18:43,900
Akala ko si Leon.

305
00:18:44,067 --> 00:18:46,200
Siya ang huling may-ari
Nakausap ko dito.

306
00:18:46,333 --> 00:18:48,033
Mm-hmm! Sir Leon?

307
00:18:48,167 --> 00:18:49,367
Oo, sir.

308
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:53,033
Si Sir Leon ang anak
ng matalik na kaibigan ni Sir Michael.

309
00:18:53,167 --> 00:18:54,333
Ah...

310
00:18:54,433 --> 00:18:56,467
Kaya ang mga bata
ng matalik na kaibigan na iyon...

311
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:58,867
sila na ba ang bagong management?
tama ba yun?

312
00:18:58,967 --> 00:19:00,333
Sakto, sir.

313
00:19:01,533 --> 00:19:04,833
Ngunit ang isang amo, si Leon...

314
00:19:04,933 --> 00:19:06,567
Medyo tahimik siya, ha?

315
00:19:06,733 --> 00:19:10,533
Sa nakikita ko, siya
yung maraming sikreto.

316
00:19:10,633 --> 00:19:11,867
Hmm.

317
00:19:11,967 --> 00:19:14,067
Inverter lang talaga siya.

318
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:16,833
- Ano?
- Oh, ibig kong sabihin... Sa...

319
00:19:16,933 --> 00:19:19,167
Isa siyang introvert.

320
00:19:19,267 --> 00:19:22,067
Anyway, sir,
may kailangan ka ba?

321
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:24,067
Hindi, magaling ako.
Salamat, Raphie.

322
00:19:24,233 --> 00:19:25,600
Okay.
[TUMITIW]

323
00:19:25,767 --> 00:19:28,000
Pupunta ako dito.
Tawagan mo ako kung kailangan mo ng tulong.

324
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,100
salamat po.

325
00:19:29,300 --> 00:19:36,267
[UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING]

326
00:19:37,733 --> 00:19:39,133
Lola?

327
00:19:40,267 --> 00:19:42,600
Naririnig mo ba ako?

328
00:19:42,767 --> 00:19:43,933
[WHIMPERS]

329
00:19:44,767 --> 00:19:46,433
[SA MABABANG BOSES]
Ang apo ko...

330
00:19:51,133 --> 00:19:53,200
Aking mahal...

331
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:57,767
Hiniram ko ang katawan ng kaibigan mo

332
00:19:58,967 --> 00:20:01,267
kaya't sa wakas ay mapayapa ka na.

333
00:20:01,433 --> 00:20:03,600
Maligayang kaarawan!

334
00:20:04,933 --> 00:20:05,967
Lola!

335
00:20:07,533 --> 00:20:09,067
Nasaan si Lolo Nando?

336
00:20:09,167 --> 00:20:15,967
[GLUM MUSIC PLAYING]

337
00:20:22,167 --> 00:20:28,933
[MUSIC BECOMING GRIM]

338
00:20:42,833 --> 00:20:43,833
Maria...

339
00:20:45,233 --> 00:20:49,033
gawin...
May nakikita ka ba?

340
00:20:49,300 --> 00:20:50,500
Ikaw!

341
00:20:51,733 --> 00:20:52,600
Ako?

342
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:55,600
May kasama kang anino.

343
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:57,300
ano?

344
00:20:57,500 --> 00:20:58,767
Anong anino?

345
00:20:58,867 --> 00:21:01,300
May nakakabit sa iyo
at galit ito.

346
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,000
Ano ito, Cheska?
Ginugulo mo ba ako?

347
00:21:05,167 --> 00:21:06,033
Hoy, hindi!

348
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:08,000
Maria, ano ka ba
pinag-uusapan?

349
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,667
Hindi ako, hindi ako.

350
00:21:11,067 --> 00:21:12,833
Mag-ingat ka.

351
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:17,367
May mga panganib
naghihintay sayo.

352
00:21:18,233 --> 00:21:21,000
At kung ano man iyon,
hindi ko alam.

353
00:21:21,100 --> 00:21:27,867
[GRIM MUSIC TULOY]

354
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:47,533
Hindi!

355
00:21:47,633 --> 00:21:49,400
Paumanhin. Pearl, pakiusap...

356
00:21:49,533 --> 00:21:51,067
Hindi ka makakaligtaan
ang pulong ng negosyo.

357
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,567
Ikaw ang huling pag-asa ko.

358
00:21:54,067 --> 00:21:55,533
Hello?

359
00:21:55,633 --> 00:21:57,367
Hello?
[LINE DISCONNECTS]

360
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:01,567
Sari. S... Sari!

361
00:22:01,700 --> 00:22:03,267
- Sari!
- Sir!

362
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,433
saan ka napunta?

363
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:07,400
Hindi ba dapat
para manatili sa tabi ko?

364
00:22:08,467 --> 00:22:09,600
Sir?

365
00:22:09,767 --> 00:22:11,900
Nandito na po ako sir.
Sa tabi mo.

366
00:22:12,067 --> 00:22:13,500
Gusto mo ba ako doon?

367
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,567
Anyway, hindi makakarating si Pearl.

368
00:22:16,733 --> 00:22:18,400
Hindi siya sasama?

369
00:22:21,467 --> 00:22:23,600
Ay hindi!

370
00:22:23,767 --> 00:22:25,933
Hindi siya sasama?

371
00:22:26,100 --> 00:22:28,433
Kaya kailangan ko ng bagong date.

372
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:32,067
Tawagan ang lahat ng kakilala mo
sino kaya ang ka-date ko.

373
00:22:32,167 --> 00:22:35,533
Siya ay dapat na kaakit-akit,
matalino, at presentable.

374
00:22:35,633 --> 00:22:36,600
Ngayon.

375
00:22:36,767 --> 00:22:43,433
[MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING]

376
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,733
Ano pang hinihintay mo?!

377
00:22:45,833 --> 00:22:47,733
Tumatawag ako ngayon, ginoo.

378
00:22:47,833 --> 00:22:54,600
[MELLOW MUSIC CONTINUES]

379
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:09,300
Sundan mo lang ako,
medyo malayo pa naman.

380
00:23:09,433 --> 00:23:11,733
- Malayo pa.
- Malayo pa, mister?

381
00:23:11,833 --> 00:23:13,133
Nakuha namin ito, nakuha namin ito.

382
00:23:13,267 --> 00:23:14,133
ayos lang.

383
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:16,467
Teka, ang sakit ng paa ko.

384
00:23:16,633 --> 00:23:18,600
- Jade, may tae!
- Saan?! [SUMIGAW si JADE]

385
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:19,800
Oh diyos ko!

386
00:23:20,967 --> 00:23:22,067
- Malapit na iyon.
- Oo.

387
00:23:22,233 --> 00:23:24,767
- Diyos ko!
- [PAWANG TAWA]

388
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:27,000
Muntik na naman kaming malas.

389
00:23:27,133 --> 00:23:28,600
- Diyos ko.
- Mabaho.

390
00:23:28,700 --> 00:23:30,167
Oo, mabaho talaga.

391
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:31,300
Mag-ingat.

392
00:23:31,467 --> 00:23:33,100
[GIGGLES]

393
00:23:38,800 --> 00:23:39,867
[MAMAHIMONG UNgol]

394
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,667
[BUMUGA NG MABUTI]

395
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:43,000
Lord, kaya ko to.

396
00:23:44,567 --> 00:23:45,767
kaya ko to.

397
00:23:47,467 --> 00:23:48,500
ginoo!

398
00:23:51,133 --> 00:23:52,667
ginoo!

399
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:54,167
Hintayin mo ako.

400
00:23:55,933 --> 00:23:57,033
Halika na.

401
00:23:57,167 --> 00:24:04,167
[HINGA NG MABUTI si EDWARD]

402
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:10,000
[LALAKI]
Nandito na tayo!

403
00:24:10,167 --> 00:24:12,367
- Talaga? Diyos ko.
- Oo!

404
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,733
Sa wakas!

405
00:24:13,867 --> 00:24:15,233
[LALAKI]
Enjoy.

406
00:24:16,167 --> 00:24:18,400
- Wow.
- Wow.

407
00:24:23,233 --> 00:24:24,700
Kiko, ang ganda.

408
00:24:39,467 --> 00:24:41,267
- [WET SQUELCH]
- [EDWARD] Ay... Ay!

409
00:24:42,467 --> 00:24:44,000
Napaka malas!

410
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:46,667
[LALAKI] Naku, sir,
natapakan mo ito.

411
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:49,333
Sigurado ka ba
dito sila pupunta?

412
00:24:49,433 --> 00:24:53,100
Oo, sir. Hindi ko sasayangin
ang pera na ibinayad mo sa akin.

413
00:24:53,233 --> 00:24:56,500
Siya nga pala, ginoo,
bakit natin sinusundan si Miss Jade?

414
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,100
Nag-aalala ako sa kanya.

415
00:25:00,233 --> 00:25:01,833
Oh, ikaw ba
Boyfriend ni Miss Jade?

416
00:25:04,067 --> 00:25:06,300
Dahil kagabi,

417
00:25:06,433 --> 00:25:10,300
Akala ko si Kiko
at si Miss Jade ay mag-asawa.

418
00:25:10,433 --> 00:25:12,567
Pero sabi nila hindi daw.

419
00:25:12,733 --> 00:25:14,233
So ikaw ang boyfriend?

420
00:25:19,267 --> 00:25:20,600
Ito ba ay isang uri ng sayaw sa araw?

421
00:25:20,733 --> 00:25:22,900
<i>Nagsasayaw kami dito at
nawawala ang ating malas?</i>

422
00:25:23,067 --> 00:25:25,200
<i> Iyan ang sinabi ni lolo.</i>

423
00:25:26,467 --> 00:25:29,100
<i>Sa hitsura nito,
Sa palagay ko hindi ito naging maganda.</i>

424
00:25:29,233 --> 00:25:31,233
<i> Kailangan nating magbayad sa bangko.</i>

425
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:33,300
<i>Nagpadala na sila ng sulat
tungkol sa utang.</i>

426
00:25:33,433 --> 00:25:35,100
<i>Mukhang kailangan natin
isang mamumuhunan.</i>

427
00:25:35,267 --> 00:25:36,600
<i> Magiging part-owner sila.</i>

428
00:25:36,767 --> 00:25:38,633
<i>Wala ka sa Maynila
para kumilos na parang thug!</i>

429
00:25:38,767 --> 00:25:41,400
<i> Uy, Luna, Solenn,
</i>o kahit anong bongga pangalan...

430
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,233
<i> wala kang pinagkaiba sa akin.</i>

431
00:25:43,333 --> 00:25:46,633
<i>Mabangis na bata, party girl...
Alam ko ang iyong maruming sikreto.</i>

432
00:25:46,767 --> 00:25:47,733
[BLOW LANDS]

